Package: spiralizer
Title: Interactive Voronoi Diagrams from Fermat Spirals
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Philipp", "Thoss", , "ph.thoss@gmx.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4672-2792"))
Description: A Shiny web application that creates beautiful Voronoi diagrams
    based on Fermat spirals. Features an interactive interface for exploring
    spiral parameters, multiple color palettes, and high-resolution export
    capabilities.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/pjt222/spiralizer,
    https://pjt222.shinyapps.io/spiralizer/
BugReports: https://github.com/pjt222/spiralizer/issues
